{"tid":2304501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"critical thinking","createTime":"2020-11-29T00:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T04:05:04.000Z","uid":312211,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe4d3d505f8cf640345b2065501b9b698a8c17a","tid":2304501,"uid":312211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T00:03:19.000Z","msg":"「林鄭月娥昨在港台《星期六問責》表示，通識科當中的「批判性思考」被異化，變成「每件事都反對才算批判性」，反問「如果你很接受有些政府講法，或者《基本法》的說法，就不夠critical（批判）？我又覺得不是」，又稱明辨慎思的基礎是客觀的知識和歷史背景，認為通識科現在多數變成討論時事，容易受某一種指導意見影響。」<br />\n<br />\n我亦想反問她「如果你很接受有些<strong>巿民大眾</strong>的講法，就不夠critical（批判）？我又覺得不是」<br />\n<br />\n她的政府永遠是對的想法，究竟到幾時先會覺醒。佢有冇讀過歷史，有幾多由上而下的決定是錯誤的決定。佢個行政會議同埋施政班底裏面有幾多個真係做得嘢？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20201129/s00001/1606586904452/%e6%8c%87%e9%80%9a%e8%ad%98%e7%84%a1%e6%a1%86%e6%9e%b6%e3%80%8c%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%80%e5%a4%a9%e5%b7%b2%e5%87%ba%e5%95%8f%e9%a1%8c%e3%80%8d-%e7%a8%b1%e6%95%99%e8%82%b2%e5%b0%88%e6%a5%ad%e9%a0%98%e8%88%aa-%e6%95%99%e5%8d%94-%e4%bb%a4%e4%ba%ba%e5%bf%83%e5%af%92\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201129%2Fs00001%2F1606586904452%2F%25e6%258c%2587%25e9%2580%259a%25e8%25ad%2598%25e7%2584%25a1%25e6%25a1%2586%25e6%259e%25b6%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e5%25b7%25b2%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%2595%258f%25e9%25a1%258c%25e3%2580%258d-%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2582%25b2%25e5%25b0%2588%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e9%25a0%2598%25e8%2588%25aa-%25e6%2595%2599%25e5%258d%2594-%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25bf%2583%25e5%25af%2592&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoR%2FtobIAPz7vP9zHpdy2ENqg%3D&h=a7e2faa4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e8%25a6%2581%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201129%2Fs00001%2F1606586904452%2F%25e6%258c%2587%25e9%2580%259a%25e8%25ad%2598%25e7%2584%25a1%25e6%25a1%2586%25e6%259e%25b6%25e3%2580%258c%25e7%25ac%25ac%25e4%25b8%2580%25e5%25a4%25a9%25e5%25b7%25b2%25e5%2587%25ba%25e5%2595%258f%25e9%25a1%258c%25e3%2580%258d-%25e7%25a8%25b1%25e6%2595%2599%25e8%2582%25b2%25e5%25b0%2588%25e6%25a5%25ad%25e9%25a0%2598%25e8%2588%25aa-%25e6%2595%2599%25e5%258d%2594-%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25bf%2583%25e5%25af%2592&h=302265bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%e8%a6%81%e8%81%9e/article/20201129/s00001/1606586904452/%e6%8c%87%e9%80%9a%e8%ad%98%e7%84%a1%e6%a1%86%e6%9e%b6%e3%80%8c%e7%ac%ac%e4%b8%80%e5%a4%a9%e5%b7%b2%e5%87%ba%e5%95%8f%e9%a1%8c%e3%80%8d-%e7%a8%b1%e6%95%99%e8%82%b2%e5%b0%88%e6%a5%ad%e9%a0%98%e8%88%aa-%e6%95%99%e5%8d%94-%e4%bb%a4%e4%ba%ba%e5%bf%83%e5%af%92</a>"},{"pid":"95cf3aceb9dc34305251488228d69b9da1107cdc","tid":2304501,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T00:04:53.000Z","msg":"條賤婦咪一樣對樣樣批評都係in denial"},{"pid":"b6331664f41807fae594ecce2dcf87ea516590ff","tid":2304501,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T00:07:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b07420ffd919ca7c26bd08df8c72de976f3b34fb","tid":2304501,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6331664f41807fae594ecce2dcf87ea516590ff","tid":2304501,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T00:07:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T00:11:42.000Z","msg":"每件事經批判性思考得出結論都係要反對<br />\n所以咁就唔係批判性思考？<br />\n猶太人反納粹德軍，係咪又係為反而反？<br />\n<br />\n唔好由個結果去推翻個過程<br />\n好明顯係邏輯錯誤"},{"pid":"9fd88a464d052ab4b5f98dc5f810c78a2f6976ae","tid":2304501,"uid":79117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T00:13:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"deb1ba536ea7e29d75f5e4c6de1972510af73956","tid":2304501,"uid":42978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T00:18:20.000Z","msg":"冇錯, 即係依家十條yes/no問題, 十條答案都係要揀no, <br />\ne.g.1. 1+1=3; 2. 2+2=5.......etc.<br />\n依佢講法就係, 你答晒no, 所以你冇critcal thinking,<br />\n咁依家到底係邊個冇critical thinking呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf7880bcf887f0777382c8e20e760f6b88ef9ee","tid":2304501,"uid":252840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T00:30:59.000Z","msg":"批判性思考就係要每件事都批判過先決定接唔接受<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪件件政策都係全部人都唔接受呢<br />\n我相信唔係<br />\n<br />\n但係政府只會睇到每件事都有人反對，因為贊成既係唔會大大聲贊成，特別係政府民望咁低既時候<br />\n<br />\n佢應該檢討既係點解贊成聲音咁細，反對聲音咁大，而唔係教人咩叫批判性思考"},{"pid":"ec658f0514f2a0d4c9ce870887c7814712979864","tid":2304501,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T00:35:28.000Z","msg":"柒婆淨係focus on output全部同一樣嘢就話有問題<br />\n刻意blur咗input全部都有問題先有咁嘅output<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"071db72586435db1ebb595bd29541cb74ffb21dd","tid":2304501,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T01:20:09.000Z","msg":"Critical Thinking譯做「明辯是非」"},{"pid":"ffec2b5377ec0634ae74b1b4ea1208e10e7b7940","tid":2304501,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-29T04:05:04.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>異化</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}